  "detailed_description": "<h1>Official Discord Server</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/1788d69b769b8b3dfe70f5df9f89b232.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/1788d69b769b8b3dfe70f5df9f89b232.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/1788d69b769b8b3dfe70f5df9f89b232.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Quack Invasion is an action game with roguelike elements. Survive each run against waves of enemies from a variety of alien ducks before they wipe out humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWER UP FOR BATTLE!</h2>Each run reveals different terrain and enemies as you go, so you'll have a selection of mechs and power ups to create the best build for every situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/12309c8ab8cd73a1e9e6c309cb37262a.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/12309c8ab8cd73a1e9e6c309cb37262a.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/12309c8ab8cd73a1e9e6c309cb37262a.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ITEMS AND LEVELS</h2>Besides powering up, using different items will help you dealing with dozens of quacks at once.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b739a8d114fab16d9f91a58810c95d61.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b739a8d114fab16d9f91a58810c95d61.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b739a8d114fab16d9f91a58810c95d61.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTERACTABLE LEVELS</h2>Terrain tiles change during a match, creating a new battlefield based on your actions and items used.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b952523de0db1ca47753f18b9eeaeb13.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b952523de0db1ca47753f18b9eeaeb13.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b952523de0db1ca47753f18b9eeaeb13.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTERING</h2>Quack Invasion is a hard game. Prepare yourself for a real challenge to win each run.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/903153d5fb092bcbdfde85b816e75d06.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/903153d5fb092bcbdfde85b816e75d06.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/903153d5fb092bcbdfde85b816e75d06.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/1788d69b769b8b3dfe70f5df9f89b232.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/1788d69b769b8b3dfe70f5df9f89b232.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/1788d69b769b8b3dfe70f5df9f89b232.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Quack Invasion is an action game with roguelike elements. Survive each run against waves of enemies from a variety of alien ducks before they wipe out humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWER UP FOR BATTLE!</h2>Each run reveals different terrain and enemies as you go, so you'll have a selection of mechs and power ups to create the best build for every situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/12309c8ab8cd73a1e9e6c309cb37262a.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/12309c8ab8cd73a1e9e6c309cb37262a.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/12309c8ab8cd73a1e9e6c309cb37262a.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ITEMS AND LEVELS</h2>Besides powering up, using different items will help you dealing with dozens of quacks at once.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b739a8d114fab16d9f91a58810c95d61.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b739a8d114fab16d9f91a58810c95d61.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b739a8d114fab16d9f91a58810c95d61.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTERACTABLE LEVELS</h2>Terrain tiles change during a match, creating a new battlefield based on your actions and items used.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b952523de0db1ca47753f18b9eeaeb13.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b952523de0db1ca47753f18b9eeaeb13.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/b952523de0db1ca47753f18b9eeaeb13.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTERING</h2>Quack Invasion is a hard game. Prepare yourself for a real challenge to win each run.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/903153d5fb092bcbdfde85b816e75d06.poster.avif?t=1747660245\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/903153d5fb092bcbdfde85b816e75d06.webm?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315490/extras/903153d5fb092bcbdfde85b816e75d06.mp4?t=1747660245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
